fortran 2003 exercise, just for my study.
like the following can be achieved.

type(matrix) :: a, b, c, d, e, f

a = matrix(size)
b = matrix(size)

call a%set_mat(-1.0d0, 1.0d0, 5555)
call b%set_mat(-2.0d0, 2.0d0, 7777)

c = a*b
d = c+a-b
e = d
f = c/b ! = c*b^-1
if (a == f) write(6, *) "A == F"

simply use C++ is enough...?

